    Discounted Rabies Vaccinations During the month of April, many local veterinarians, in cooperation with Carteret County Animal Control, will offer discounted rabies vaccines for dogs, cats, and ferrets for $7.00 beginning on April 1 and ending on April 30. **Contact veterinarian offices for hours and appointments** Participating Veterinarians: -Austin Veterinary, 1550 Lennoxville Road, Beaufort, (252) 838-9028 -Brigadoon Animal Hospital, 1074 Cedar Point Boulevard, Cedar Point, (252) 393-6581 -Island Pets Veterinary ...

  5. Tue Apr. 30

    Carteret Food & Health Council Public Forum Are you interested are you interested in food and in the health and wellness of our community? If so, we would like to invite you to a public forum about the Carteret Food and Health Council. The Task Force has been working to create a food and health council. Now, all that's missing is you! We hope to see you on April 30th. light refreshments will be provided from 5:30pm-6:00pm! Registration: https://www.surveymonkey.com/r/CFHCpublicforum
